desc=Humans come in a broad variety of shapes and sizes. An average Human male in good health stands around six feet tall and weighs around 175 pounds, while females average five feet nine inches and weigh around 145 pounds. Most Humans live around 75 years.//Humans may be any single class, other than the combination classes. They have no minimum or maximum ability score requirements.//Humans learn unusually quickly, gaining a bonus of 10 percent to all experience points earned.

