desc=Bugbears look like huge, hairy goblins, standing about 6 feet tall. Their eyes are usually a darkish brown color. Bugbears can move very quietly, but are wild and relatively fearless, and bully smaller humanoids whenever possible.//Bugbears prefer to ambush opponents if they can. When hunting, they often send scouts ahead of the main group. Bugbear attacks are coordinated, and their tactics are sound if not brilliant. They are able to move in nearly complete silence, gaining a large bonus to their `movesilently` skill roll, if a thief or scout. Finally, a Bugbear has a Darkvision out to 60'.

