desc=Orcs are grotesque humanoids bent on war and domination. They have lupine ears, reddish eyes, truncated, upturned noses, and black hair (but very little body hair). An adult male orc is a little over 6' tall and weighs about 210 pounds; females are slightly smaller. An orc prefers to wear vivid colors that many humans would consider unpleasant. Orcs utilize all manner of weapons and armor scavenged from battlefields. They speak their own rough and simple language, but many also speak some Common or Goblin.//Orcs have Darkvision out to 60 feet.

